definition: to succeed/to finish/to complete/to accomplish/to become/to turn into/to be all right/OK!/one tenth
not according with decorum (idiom); scandalous/bad form/unacceptable behavior

sentences.english: With eight, very loosely related chapters, this book is hard to classify.
sentences.chinese: 這本書的八章自成體系，很難分出等級。

sentences.english: Short trousers are not proper at a dance.
sentences.chinese: 舞會上穿短褲不成體統。

sentences.english: He did not look at the woman as he spoke. It would not have been seemly .
sentences.chinese: 他說話的時候，沒有去看女人，因爲那是不成體統的。

sentences.english: The problem with Establishment Republicans is they abhor the unseemliness of a political brawl.
sentences.chinese: 共和黨的人問題是他們厭惡不成體統的政治上的爭鬥。

sentences.english: My handwriting has gone down with using the computer so much.
sentences.chinese: 用電腦太多，我的字寫得不成體統了。

sentences.english: Wisdom is the human ability of observation, a character a compound of many things .
sentences.chinese: 智慧是人類的洞察力，是品格，是衆多事物的合成體。

sentences.english: In late March, the synthetic genome started to produce a new form of cells.
sentences.chinese: 在三月下旬，合成體基因組開始製造一個新型的細胞。

sentences.english: Short trousers are improper at a dance.
sentences.chinese: 舞會上穿短褲不成體統。

sentences.english: It's considered improper to be unclothed in public.
sentences.chinese: 在公共場合赤身裸體被認爲是不成體統的。

sentences.english: Spain is a composite of multifarious traditions and people.
sentences.chinese: 西班牙是多種傳統和多個民族的合成體。

sentences.english: We measured the sexual dimorphism and female individual fecundity in a population of Paracanthobrama guichenoti, from Oujiang river, Lishui city, Zhejiang province.
sentences.chinese: 測定了似刺鯿鮈成體的兩性異形和雌性個體生育力。

sentences.english: RNM has comprised one system itself and proven by high-tech test already.
sentences.chinese: 該套方法自成體系，已經現代高科技測試證明。

sentences.english: Mister Venter says Synthia is a new species.
sentences.chinese: 文特爾先生說合成體是一個新的物種。

sentences.english: It wasn't quite the done thing for women to drink in pubs in those days.
sentences.chinese: 那年月女的到酒店喝酒可不成體統。

sentences.english: She behaved very badly at the party.
sentences.chinese: 她在聚會上的舉止真不成體統。

sentences.english: The quantity of Copepoda occupied a considerable proportion in each month.
sentences.chinese: 撓足類擬成體的數量在各月份中佔相當大的比例。
